  "prompt": "Kindly suggest the best NPTE classes in NY?",
  "response": "When preparing for the **National Physical Therapy Examination (NPTE)**, it\u2019s essential to choose a course that aligns with your learning style and provides comprehensive resources. Here are some of the best NPTE prep classes and resources available in New York and online:\n\n---\n\n### **1. TherapyEd (Scorebuilders)**\n   - **Location**: Online, but widely used by students in NY.\n   - **Why it\u2019s great**: TherapyEd is one of the most popular NPTE prep providers. Their study materials include detailed textbooks, online quizzes, and simulated exams. They also offer live review courses in various locations, including NY.\n   - **Website**: [www.therapyed.com](https://www.therapyed.com)\n\n---\n\n### **2. PT Final Exam**\n   - **Location**: Online and in-person options available.\n   - **Why it\u2019s great**: PT Final Exam offers a structured online review course with video lectures, practice questions, and study schedules. Their materials are tailored to help you focus on high-yield topics.\n   - **Website**: [www.ptfinalexam.com](https://www.ptfinalexam.com)\n\n---\n\n### **3. PT Hustle Week**\n   - **Location**: Online, but highly recommended by NY students.\n   - **Why it\u2019s great**: This intensive 1-week online program focuses on high-yield content and test-taking strategies. It\u2019s designed for students who want a quick but effective review.\n   - **Website**: [www.pthustle.com](https://www.pthustle.com)\n\n---\n\n### **4. Base PT**\n   - **Location**: Online.\n   - **Why it\u2019s great**: Base PT offers a digital course with video lectures, flashcards, and practice questions. Their approach is student-friendly and covers all major topics tested on the NPTE.\n   - **Website**: [www.basept.com](https://www.basept.com)\n\n---\n\n### **5. Local University Resources**\n   - Many PT schools in NY, such as **Columbia University**, **NYU**, and **Stony Brook University**, offer their own review courses or study groups for students preparing for the NPTE. Check with your school\u2019s PT department for available resources.\n\n---\n\n### **6. Kaplan NPTE Prep**\n   - **Location**: Online.\n   - **Why it\u2019s great**: Kaplan is a trusted name in test prep. Their NPTE course includes live online classes, practice exams, and study materials.\n   - **Website**: [www.kaptest.com](https://www.kaptest.com)\n\n---\n\n### **Tips for Choosing the Right Course:**\n   - Consider your learning style (live classes vs. self-paced online courses).\n   - Look for courses with practice exams and detailed explanations.\n   - Check reviews and testimonials from past students.\n   - Ensure the course covers the latest NPTE content outline.\n\nGood luck with your NPTE preparation!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
